marcd-0.7.7
-----------

  * Improved configuration handling.

marcd-0.7.6
-----------

  * Added support for syslog and daemonization.
  * Adding bundled iniparser for platforms without package. (not recommended,
    must be explicitly requested)
  * Lots of bug- and regressionfixes.

marcd-0.7.5
-----------

  * allow program name transformation

marcd-0.7.4
-----------

* compability with libcap_utils-0.7.4

marcd-0.7.3
-----------

* [relay] 64bit compability.
* [relay] better compability with legacy MPs.
